    "description": "经过几个月的调查，还是没人能找到你的兄弟，当所有希望都破灭后，你决定亲自展开行动。为此你将独自前往那些令人极度不安的地方，通过调查找出真相，注意，整个过程中必须要特别小心，因为在这场犹如噩梦般的旅程里潜藏着无数的危险。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1092530/extras/bbd5a0796b6fb0f9dacac5adbd221d10.poster.avif?t=1726695619\" width=616 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1092530/extras/bbd5a0796b6fb0f9dacac5adbd221d10.webm?t=1726695619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1092530/extras/bbd5a0796b6fb0f9dacac5adbd221d10.mp4?t=1726695619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1092530/extras/e8ce39d775d8deb7f21e318419f040d1.webp?t=1726695619\" width=616 height=62 /></span><br>随着故事章节不断推进，你会逐渐发现，每一个看似独立的恐怖故事，最终都指向了某个共同的悲剧。而整个探索过程也在揭示着人类潜意识中最本能的恐惧，你必须战胜它们，才可能找到你的兄弟。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1092530/extras/66ffabd66946b5e42870bbb9718e2e32.poster.avif?t=1726695619\" width=616 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1092530/extras/66ffabd66946b5e42870bbb9718e2e32.webm?t=1726695619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1092530/extras/66ffabd66946b5e42870bbb9718e2e32.mp4?t=1726695619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1092530/extras/1492209f3ad7b9f44242b3b855223d55.webp?t=1726695619\" width=616 height=62 /></span><br>在调查指引下，你将会深入一个被废弃的医疗机构。进而逐步了解到这里曾发生过的恐怖过往，以及与之有关的人后来究竟遭遇了什么。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1092530/extras/79c86de8a6efb213d0691aab68892627.poster.avif?t=1726695619\" width=616 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1092530/extras/79c86de8a6efb213d0691aab68892627.webm?t=1726695619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1092530/extras/79c86de8a6efb213d0691aab68892627.mp4?t=1726695619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1092530/extras/41a4112a88b6c2875a77de2ec228fe17.webp?t=1726695619\" width=616 height=62 /></span><br>通过研究那些与你兄弟失踪有关的记忆，你将会体验到许多无法解释的超自然现象，并在难以想象的空间中努力求生，最后才能将收集到的碎片一点点拼凑起来。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1092530/extras/dae6341cb9fe4ecbbcf4c24049eaaafc.poster.avif?t=1726695619\" width=616 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1092530/extras/dae6341cb9fe4ecbbcf4c24049eaaafc.webm?t=1726695619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1092530/extras/dae6341cb9fe4ecbbcf4c24049eaaafc.mp4?t=1726695619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1092530/extras/f82fa8b88645e5d3b27e2069ead07bef.webp?t=1726695619\" width=616 height=62 /></span><br>在通往真相的道路上，有许多危险需要你去应对。积极在场景中寻找可互动的线索，并合理的利用那些超自然现象，将有助于你搞清楚究竟发生了什么。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_asse